	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Some of SNES games that have electric guitar sounds, I notice there's a programmed in vibrato to enhance the samples.  I think it is a special type of vibrato, like it starts out fast, then slow, then medium, and there might be some overal pitch bend as well.  I think there's funky going on with ADSR envelopes as well, but it's hard to discribe, like having two peaks before &quot;sustaining.&quot;

		

